---
import { ArrowRight, CheckCircle2, Phone } from '@lucide/astro';
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Contact ACC Building Performance | Book Your Assessment"
  description="Contact ACC Building Performance to book a building science assessment, compliance test, HVAC design, or healthy home consultation in Louisiana, Mississippi, Alabama, and the Gulf South."
>
  <section class="hero-airflow hero-noise relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-[#0b4850] px-5 py-24 text-white sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-32">
    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <p class="text-[0.62rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#86c8dc] sm:text-[0.72rem] sm:tracking-[0.34em]">Contact</p>
      <h1 class="mt-8 max-w-4xl text-5xl font-black leading-[0.98] tracking-tight sm:text-7xl">Let's Find the Answer Your Home Has Been Waiting For.</h1>
      <p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-white/63">Fill out the form below and AJ will follow up with you personally. No automated systems. No call centers. A real conversation with the person who will actually do the work.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-acc-mist px-5 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl items-start gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.55fr]">
      <form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="company" class="rounded-2xl border border-[#d5ded9] bg-white p-7 shadow-2xl shadow-[#06333a]/10 sm:p-9">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
        <p class="hidden"><label>Company <input name="company" /></label></p>
        <div class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">First Name *<input name="first_name" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Last Name *<input name="last_name" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Email Address *<input type="email" name="email" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Phone Number *<input type="tel" name="phone" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">City / State *<input name="city_state" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">
            What type of home do you have?
            <select name="home_type" class="form-field">
              <option>Single-family home</option>
              <option>New construction</option>
              <option>Renovation project</option>
              <option>I'm a contractor</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">
            What are you experiencing?
            <select name="situation_type" class="form-field">
              <option>Unexplained illness</option>
              <option>Mold or moisture concerns</option>
              <option>HVAC performance issues</option>
              <option>Planning a new build</option>
              <option>Need compliance testing</option>
              <option>HVAC design services</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">
            Tell us about your situation in your own words:
            <textarea name="message" rows="8" class="form-field resize-y"></textarea>
          </label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">
            How did you hear about us?
            <select name="referral_source" class="form-field">
              <option>Doctor referral</option>
              <option>Friend or family</option>
              <option>Google</option>
              <option>Social media</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
          </label>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="mt-7 inline-flex min-h-14 items-center gap-2 rounded-lg btn-gold px-8 text-base font-extrabold shadow-sm transition">
          Send My Message
          <ArrowRight class="h-5 w-5" />
        </button>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm font-bold leading-6 text-[#5c7178]">After you submit, AJ will follow up by phone or email within one business day. If your situation is urgent, you are also welcome to call or text directly.</p>
        <a href="tel:+15042480186" class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-black text-[#0b6b78]"><Phone class="h-5 w-5" />504-248-0186</a>
      </form>

      <aside class="grid gap-6">
        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-[#d5ded9] bg-white p-7 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#063f46]">What Happens Next</h2>
          <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
            {[
              'You submit the form.',
              'AJ reviews your information and reaches out personally, typically within one business day.',
              'You have a real conversation about your home, your situation, and whether an assessment is the right next step.',
              'If you move forward, we send you an intake form and get your assessment scheduled.',
            ].map((step) => (
              <p class="flex gap-3 text-sm font-bold leading-6 text-[#365563]">
                <CheckCircle2 class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-[#0b6b78]" />
                <span>{step}</span>
              </p>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-[#5c7178]">There's no pressure. No sales pitch. Just a straight conversation with someone who genuinely wants to help you figure out what's going on.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-2xl bg-[#06333a] p-7 text-white shadow-2xl shadow-[#06333a]/20 ring-1 ring-white/10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black">A Note From AJ</h2>
          <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white/75">
            <p>When you reach out to ACC Building Performance, you're not entering a sales funnel. You're starting a conversation with me directly.</p>
            <p>I know you've probably tried other things. I know you may have spent money that didn't produce results. I know you might be skeptical about whether this is going to be any different.</p>
            <p>What I can tell you is this: if something is wrong with your home, I will find it. I will document it clearly. And I will tell you exactly what it means and what needs to happen about it, honestly, directly, and without any agenda other than getting you the right answer.</p>
            <p class="font-black text-white">AJ, ACC Building Performance</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-[#d5ded9] bg-white p-7 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#063f46]">Serving These Areas</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base font-bold leading-7 text-[#365563]">Louisiana | Mississippi | Alabama | Gulf South Region</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-[#5c7178]">Don't see your area listed? Reach out anyway. We may still be able to help or refer you to a qualified resource.</p>
        </section>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
